GSD.description:
NFSv4.2: Fix a memory stomp in decode_attr_security_label

This is an automated ID intended to aid in discovery of potential security vulnerabilities. The actual impact and attack plausibility have not yet been proven.
This ID is fixed in Linux Kernel version v5.10.163 by commit 15feece7afcff25766a66aacc380652eebc0a114, it was introduced in version v5.9 by commit b4487b93545214a9db8cbf32e86411677b0cca21. For more details please see the references link.
